No. 10-537. Osage Nation, Petitioner v. Constance Irby, Secretary-Member of the Oklahoma Tax Commission, et al. 564 U.S. 1046, 131 S. Ct. 3056,

180 L. Ed. 2d 902,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 4986. June 27, 2011.

Petition for writ of cer-tiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Tenth Circuit denied.

Justice Kagan took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.

Same case below, 597 F.3d 1117.
